  <summary>4/12/2011--Introduced.
Recognizes the brave service of all members of Brigada de Asalto 2506 (Assault Brigade 2506), both living and deceased, involved in the 1961 Bay of Pigs operation in Cuba. Calls on the United States to continue policies that promote respect for the fundamental principles of freedom, democracy, and human rights in Cuba.</summary>
